<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Error - Something Went Wrong</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fff3f3;
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 5rem;
      color: #dc3545;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #dc3545;
      border: 1px solid #dc3545;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: #dc3545;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <h2>Something went wrong!</h2>
    <p>  an unexpected error occurred.<br>Please try again later or go back to the homepage.</p>
    <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
